data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER...WILL ENTERTAIN ANY REASONABLE OFFER!! Unexpectedly, needing to relocate . Come tour this 2208sf immaculate 4 bedroom/3 bath ranch style home in Somersby Pointe. Closest thing to being new construction you can get at only 5 months old and looks like it did the day it was purchased. Nice open floorpan when you walk through the door with dining area ,living area and kitchen making it a perfect gathering place big enough for a large family or entertaining. Split floorpan with master on one side and the additional three bedrooms (one with ensuite) on the other . Some of the features include luxury vinyl flooring, crown moulding, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, tabby fireplace surround with coastal mantle, custom shaker style cabinets, large laundry room, new epoxy floor in garage, new kids playhouse and much more. Relax on the covered back patio in your very private back yard. One of the better lots as no one will build behind you. Short walk to schools and close to Interstate for easy travel to Jacksonville or Savannah. USDA Eligible !!     **Sellers preferred lender, Lower Mortgage, will also offer additional financing incentives with an accepted offer financed through them. Prospective buyer eligible to receive either a 1-0 Temporary Rate Buydown, or a Lender Credit to be able to be used towards Closing Costs and Title Fees...AND free re-fi's
